<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَيَا سَيِّدِي لا تُخْزِنِي فِي صَحِيفَتِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>إِذَا نُشِرَتْ يَوْمَ الْحِسَابِ الصَّحَائِفُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَكُنْ مُؤْنِسِي فِي ظُلْمَةِ الْقَبْرِ عِنْدَمَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يُصَدِّدُ ذُو الْقُرْبَى وَيَجْفُوا الْمُؤَآلِفُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>لَئِنْ ضَاقَ عَنِّي عَفْوُكَ الْوَاسِعُ الَّذِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أُرَجِيّ لإِسْرَافِي فَإِنِّي لَتَالِفُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">آخر:</span> ... غَفَلتُ وَلَيْسَ الْمَوْتُ فِي غَفْلَةٍ عَنِّي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمَا أَحَدٌ يَجْنِي عَليَّ كَمَا أَجْنِي<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أُشَيِّدُ بُنْيَانِي وَأَعْلَمُ أَنَّنِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>أَزُولُ لِمَنْ شَيَّدتُهُ وَلِمَنْ أَبْنِي<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>كَفَانِي بِالْمَوْتِ الْمُنَغَّصِ وَاعِظًا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>بِمَا أَبْصَرَتْ عَيْنِي وَمَا سَمِعَتْ أُذُنِي<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَكَمْ لِلْمَنَايَا مِنْ فُنُونٍ كَثِيرَة<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تُمِيتُ وَقَدْ وَطَّنْتُ نَفْسِي عَلَى فَنِّ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَلَوْ طَرَقَتْ مَا اسْتَأْذَنَتْ مَنْ يُحِبني<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>كَمَا أَفْقَدَتْنِي مَنْ أُحِبُّ بِلا إِذْنِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>قَدْ كُنْتُ أَفْدِي نَاظِريهِ مِنَ الْقَذَى<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَغَطَّيْتُ مَا قَدْ كُنْتُ أُفْدِيهِ بِالْعَيْنِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>سَتَسْجُني يَا رَبِّ فِي الْقَبْرِ بُرْهَةً<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَلا تَجْعَلَ النِّيرَانَ مِنْ بَعْدِهِ سِجْنِي<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَلِي عِنْدَ رَبِّي سَيِّئَاتٌ كَثِيرَةٌ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>وَلَكِنَّنِي عِبدٌ بِهِ حَسَنُ الظَّنِّ<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>